# ── SITE MISSION ──────────────────────────────────────────────
# GeoSurveyHub is a FREE educational platform for the surveying,
# GIS, and geospatial industry. It does NOT sell equipment.
# It educates, guides, and connects — then routes interested
# readers to a financing/interest form.
#
# Three pillars:
#   1. EDUCATE  — explain every technology from zero to expert
#   2. GUIDE    — help anyone figure out what they need
#   3. CONNECT  — financing form for people ready to act
# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────


# ════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
# SECTION 1 — DESIGN SYSTEM (MNTN TEMPLATE, NON-NEGOTIABLE)
# ════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════

## COLOR PALETTE — exact hex, zero deviation allowed
```css
:root {
  --bg:           #0B1D26;
  --surface:      #162535;
  --surface2:     #1C2F3D;
  --surface3:     #0f1e2a;
  --white:        #FFFFFF;
  --muted:        #7A8B99;
  --accent:       #FBD784;
  --accent-dim:   #C9A55A;
  --accent-glow:  rgba(251,215,132,0.08);
  --border:       rgba(255,255,255,0.07);
  --border-mid:   rgba(255,255,255,0.12);
  --border-accent:rgba(251,215,132,0.25);
}
```

## TYPOGRAPHY
- Display/H1/H2: Playfair Display serif — italic for emphasis words in em tags
- UI/Nav/Kickers/Labels/Buttons: Barlow Condensed sans-serif
- Body paragraphs: Barlow sans-serif weight 300
- Code/Specs/Coords/Numbers: Space Mono monospace
- Google Fonts: https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Playfair+Display:ital,wght@0,700;1,400&family=Barlow:wght@300;400;500&family=Barlow+Condensed:wght@400;500;600&family=Space+Mono&display=swap

## LAYOUT CONSTANTS
- Max content width: 1200px centered
- Section padding: 120px vertical / 60px horizontal
- Text column max-width: 440px
- MNTN alternating sections: grid 1fr 1fr, direction:rtl for reverse
- Dividers: 1px solid var(--border) — never hr tags
- Border-radius: 2px for buttons/badges, 4px for cards/panels
- NO box-shadows, NO gradients on backgrounds, NO white backgrounds

## AESTHETIC REQUIREMENTS — STRICTLY ENFORCED
Every page MUST have:
  - A full-viewport hero with SVG background (terrain/grid/crosshair motif)
  - Kicker labels: 11px, 5px letter-spacing, uppercase, accent color, 32px line prefix
  - Section numbers (01/02/03) above each major section
  - Playfair Display headlines with at least one italic accent word in em tags
  - "Read More" links with arrow suffix and gap-grow hover animation
  - Vertical side-text on hero (writing-mode: vertical-rl)
  - Scroll indicator bottom-left on hero
  - Step dots bottom-right on hero
  - Brands/partners row muted then brightens on hover
  - Full 4-column footer

Pages must feel like precision instruments: dark, calibrated, purposeful.
Every section needs visual breathing room. Never crowd content.
SVG icons throughout: stroke var(--accent), fill none, stroke-width 1.


