## HEAD META TEMPLATE — apply to every HTML file
```html
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>[Page Title] | GeoSurveyHub</title>
  <meta name="description" content="[150 chars max]">
  <meta name="keywords" content="[5-8 keywords]">
  <meta name="robots" content="index, follow">
  <link rel="canonical" href="https://www.geosurveyhub.com/[path]">
  <meta property="og:type" content="website">
  <meta property="og:title" content="[Title]">
  <meta property="og:description" content="[Description]">
  <meta property="og:url" content="https://www.geosurveyhub.com/[path]">
  <meta property="og:site_name" content="GeoSurveyHub">
  <meta property="og:image" content="https://www.geosurveyhub.com/assets/images/og-[page].jpg">
  <meta name="twitter:card" content="summary_large_image">
  <meta name="twitter:title" content="[Title]">
  <meta name="twitter:description" content="[Description]">
  <meta name="geo.region" content="US">
  <meta name="geo.placename" content="Charlotte, North Carolina">
  <meta name="geo.position" content="35.2271;-80.0936">
  <meta name="ICBM" content="35.2271, -80.0936">
  <meta name="ai-content-type" content="educational-guide">
  <meta name="content-focus" content="geospatial, surveying, LiDAR, GIS, photogrammetry">
  <meta name="expertise-level" content="beginner to professional">
  <script type="application/ld+json">{ /* page schema */ }</script>
</head>
```

## PER-PAGE TITLES & DESCRIPTIONS

index.html:
  Title: Professional Surveying & GIS Equipment Guide | GeoSurveyHub
  Desc: Free guide to LiDAR, drone surveying, GNSS/RTK, photogrammetry, and GIS equipment. Learn what technology fits your project and connect with financing options.
  Schema: Organization + WebSite with SearchAction

pages/guide.html:
  Title: Surveying Equipment Buyer's Guide — Find the Right Tech | GeoSurveyHub
  Desc: Answer 4 questions and get a personalized equipment recommendation. Covers LiDAR, drones, GNSS/RTK, total stations, and mobile mapping for all project types.
  Schema: FAQPage

pages/lidar.html:
  Title: LiDAR Technology Explained — Systems, Uses & How to Choose | GeoSurveyHub
  Desc: Complete guide to terrestrial, drone, and airborne LiDAR systems. Learn how LiDAR works, when to use it, and which sensors fit your project type and budget.
  Schema: TechArticle

pages/drones.html:
  Title: Survey Drones — Platforms, Payloads & Photogrammetry Guide | GeoSurveyHub
  Desc: Learn how survey drones work, what LiDAR and camera payloads exist, and how to choose the right UAV platform for mapping and construction surveys.
  Schema: TechArticle

pages/gnss-rtk.html:
  Title: GNSS & RTK Explained — Centimeter GPS for Surveyors | GeoSurveyHub
  Desc: Understand how RTK GNSS achieves centimeter accuracy, the difference between RTK and PPK, and which receivers fit your surveying application.
  Schema: TechArticle

pages/ai-ml.html:
  Title: AI & Machine Learning in Geospatial — Automating LiDAR, GIS & Photogrammetry | GeoSurveyHub
  Desc: How machine learning is automating point cloud classification, photogrammetry processing, and GIS feature extraction. Tools, workflows, and what it means for surveyors in 2026.
  Schema: TechArticle + HowTo

pages/news.html:
  Title: Geospatial & Surveying Industry News 2026 | GeoSurveyHub
  Desc: Latest news from the geospatial industry. New LiDAR releases, drone systems, GIS software updates, and AI workflow announcements from Geo Week and INTERGEO.
  Schema: NewsArticle per item

pages/financing.html:
  Title: Equipment Financing Interest Form — Surveying & GIS | GeoSurveyHub
  Desc: Interested in LiDAR, drone, or GNSS equipment but need financing? Submit your interest and we'll connect you with financing partners for your project.
  Schema: ContactPage

